*** Command Entries
 org 0
X$SPRC rmb 2 Search directory for procedure
X$EREX rmb 2 Print error messsage and return
X$SEXT rmb 2 Set (error) exit address
X$EXIT rmb 2 Exit via (error) exit address
X$SBST rmb 2 Search for substring
X$KILL rmb 2 Kill external procedure
X$BYE  rmb 2 exit basic09, give up workspace
X$KALL rmb 2 kill all external procs
X$SKST rmb 2 Skip to next logical icode stmt beginning
 ifne INCLUDED&EDITOR

X$LKTK rmb 2 Lookup token in decompile table
X$RPLC rmb 2 Replace i-code
X$PBLN rmb 2 Print a bound line
X$DBUG rmb 2 Enter debug state
X$TEXP rmb 2 Trace expression address
X$TEXR rmb 2 Trace result
 endc

*** Compiler Entries
 org 0
X$CPRM rmb 2 Compile parameter list
X$NAME rmb 2 Look for a name subroutine
X$SRCH rmb 2 Table search subroutine
X$MVDN rmb 2 Block move down subroutine
 ifne INCLUDED&EDITOR

X$EXDS rmb 2 Expand desr tbl
X$CMPL rmb 2 Line compiler
 endc

*** Binder Entries
